    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Populus canescens, native to Europe but introduced to North America. It is light-yellow in color and used for carpentry and flooring.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
